atigue but limits performance insights.<\/p>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1294\" data-end=\"1458\"><strong data-start=\"1294\" data-end=\"1314\">Better approach:<\/strong> Test multiple creatives (images, videos, carousels), headlines, and call-to-actions to find what drives the highest engagement and conversions.<\/p>\n<h3 class=\"\" data-start=\"1460\" data-end=\"1501\">4. Ignoring Landing Page Experience<\/h3>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1502\" data-end=\"1610\">Running a great ad but linking to a slow, irrelevant, or poorly designed website kills conversion potential.<\/p>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1612\" data-end=\"1754\"><strong data-start=\"1612\" data-end=\"1632\">Better approach:<\/strong> Align your landing page with your ad\u2019s message. Ensure it\u2019s fast, mobile-optimised, and has a clear call to action (CTA).<\/p>\n<h3 class=\"\" data-start=\"1756\" data-end=\"1796\">5. No Pixel or Conversion Tracking<\/h3>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1797\" data-end=\"1936\">Many Kenyan businesses don\u2019t install Meta Pixel or set up conversion events\u2014meaning they can\u2019t track leads, purchases, or measure real ROI.<\/p>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1938\" data-end=\"2072\"><strong data-start=\"1938\" data-end=\"1958\">Better approach:<\/strong> Set up Meta Pixel with standard and custom conversion events. Use this data to optimise and retarget effectively.<\/p>\n<h3 class=\"\" data-start=\"2074\" data-end=\"2105\">6. Poor Budget Allocation<\/h3>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"2106\" data-end=\"2211\">Either spending too little for meaningful results or overspending without performance tracking is common.<\/p>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"2213\" data-end=\"2390\"><strong data-start=\"2213\" data-end=\"2233\">Better approach:<\/strong> Start with a reasonable test budget and scale based on performance. Always monitor cost-per-click (CPC), cost-per-lead (CPL), and return on ad spend (ROAS).<\/p>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"2397\" data-end=\"2624\"><strong data-start=\"2397\" data-end=\"2413\">Bottom line:<\/strong> Social media advertising is only effective when it\u2019s managed with intent, skill, and data. Avoiding these mistakes is the first step to turning Meta ads into a high-performing sales and lead generation channel.<\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column_inner][\/vc_row_inner][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner][vc_column_text css=&#8221;&#8221;]<\/p>\n<h2 class=\"\" data-start=\"145\" data-end=\"203\">Aminifu Digital\u2019s Facebook &amp; Instagram Advertising Services<\/h2>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"205\" data-end=\"491\">At <a href=\"https:\/\/aminifudigital.co.ke\/\">Aminifu Digital Agency<\/a>, we don\u2019t run ads for the sake of it. We design and manage data-driven, results-oriented Meta campaigns tailored to your business goals. Using Meta&#8217;s advanced targeting tools, our approach to Facebook and Instagram advertising in Kenya includes building high-intent audiences, making it ideal for lead generation, online sales, driving app intalls and end-to-end campaigns.<\/p>\n<h3 class=\"\" data-start=\"493\" data-end=\"522\">1. Strategy Development<\/h3>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"523\" data-end=\"616\">We begin every campaign with a deep understanding of your business, audience, and objectives.<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"618\" data-end=\"839\">\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"618\" data-end=\"652\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"620\" data-end=\"652\">Market and competitor analysis<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"653\" data-end=\"692\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"655\" data-end=\"692\">Audience profiling and segmentation<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"693\" data-end=\"769\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"695\" data-end=\"769\">Clear campaign objectives (e.g. conversions, traffic, reach, engagement)<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"770\" data-end=\"839\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"772\" data-end=\"839\">Funnel mapping: awareness, considera